title: Hey first-years, can't wait to see you there!

Attention Computer Science 1st years! The McMaster Computer Science Society is hosting their first Queries & Code event this Thursday, September 24th from 7:00-8:30 pm on the official Computer Science Society discord https://discord.gg/G7Tr43z. This week we're focusing on Haskell concepts from COMPSCI 1JC3. See you there!
